OL,3,CLorry driver wins #5.2m lottery prize
OL,4,Cso quits job and buys vacuum cleaner
OL,6,FAn east London lorry driver, who
OL,7,Fscooped #5.2 million on the lottery,
OL,8,Fquit his job and bought a new vacuum
OL,9,Fcleaner - but not before making sure
OL,10,Fhe was getting a bargain.
OL,12,FGary MacDonald, of Barking, opted for
OL,13,Fa Shark vacuum and said: "We still
OL,14,Fshopped around for the best deal on
OL,15,Fthe vacuum cleaner.
OL,17,F"We are not flash people; we are very
OL,18,Fdown to earth and know the value of
OL,19,Fthings."
