OL,3,CLorry driver wins #5.2m lottery prize
OL,4,Cso quits job and buys vacuum cleaner
OL,6,FThe 60-year-old rang his boss to
OL,7,Fresign after learning of his Lotto
OL,8,Fjackpot win.
OL,10,FHe plans to marry his partner of 25
OL,11,Fyears, Anita, aged 55, and they have
OL,12,Fbegun house-hunting for a place with a
OL,13,Flarge garden away from the city.
OL,15,FMr MacDonald, who has been delivering
OL,16,Fparcels to Lakeside Shopping Centre in
OL,17,FThurrock, Essex, for more than 30
OL,18,Fyears, learned of his win last
OL,19,FThursday.
