OL,3,CLorry driver wins #5.2m lottery prize
OL,4,Cso quits job and buys vacuum cleaner
OL,6,FHe got up at 5.20am to start his
OL,7,Fworking day and spotted an email from
OL,8,FThe National Lottery stating: "Good
OL,9,Fnews about your ticket."
OL,11,FHe was initially delighted to discover
OL,12,Fhe had won #35, then realised there
OL,13,Fwas an additional prize of more than
OL,14,F#5.2 million.
OL,16,F"It is difficult to make sense of it,"
OL,17,Fsaid Mr MacDonald.
OL,19,F"It said I had won #5,208,504 and to
OL,20,F'please call The National Lottery
OL,21,Fstraight away'.
