OL,6,F"Anita thought it was five thousand
OL,7,Fand something.
OL,9,F"I was saying: 'No love, it's more
OL,10,Fthan that.'
OL,12,F"I tried calling but of course the
OL,13,Fline was closed at 5.30 in the morning!
OL,15,F"I've always been a laid-back person
OL,16,Fbut that was the longest two and a
OL,17,Fhalf hours of my life waiting until
OL,18,Fthe phone lines open at 8.00am.
