OL,3,CLorry driver wins #5.2m lottery prize
OL,4,Cso quits job and buys vacuum cleaner
OL,6,F"It dawned on me that there was
OL,7,Fabsolutely no point in doing another
OL,8,Fday's work, not today, not any day.
OL,10,F"So, at 6.30am, I called my boss and
OL,11,Fresigned.
OL,13,F"I had been thinking about slowing
OL,14,Fdown for the last five or six years.
OL,16,F"I have always worked and enjoyed what
OL,17,FI do, but it is physically hard work."
