OL,3,CLorry driver wins #5.2m lottery prize
OL,4,Cso quits job and buys vacuum cleaner
OL,6,FOnce his win was confirmed Mr
OL,7,FMacDonald shared the good news with
OL,8,Ffamily members, including his
OL,9,Fdaughter, who thought he was teasing.
OL,11,F"It's been a crazy few days, I can't
OL,12,Fbelieve everyone's reaction," he said.
OL,14,F"I don't think I have ever been sworn
OL,15,Fat so much ` the air has definitely
OL,16,Fbeen blue in Essex."
