OL,3,CLorry driver wins #5.2m lottery prize
OL,4,Cso quits job and buys vacuum cleaner
OL,6,FHe was already planning to marry his
OL,7,Fpartner in a civil ceremony later in
OL,8,Fthe year, but has brought this forward
OL,9,Fto the summer with plans to make it a
OL,10,Fbigger celebration.
OL,12,FThe keen Formula One fan also plans to
OL,13,Fgo to watch a race in person.
OL,15,F"We have worked hard all our lives and
OL,16,Fnever really had time for hobbies or
OL,17,Fpastimes," he said.
OL,19,F"Any spare time has been spent
OL,20,Fsupporting others, we were brought up
OL,21,Fto put others first.
