OL,3,CLorry driver wins #5.2m lottery prize
OL,4,Cso quits job and buys vacuum cleaner
OL,6,F"It will be amazing to have the time
OL,7,Fand money to now treat ourselves a
OL,8,Flittle and maybe try something new.
OL,10,F"Just this morning I thought maybe I
OL,11,Fmight try lawn bowls!"
OL,13,FMr MacDonald said he has played Lotto
OL,14,Feach week since the game started and
OL,15,Fnow plays online.
OL,17,FHis winning numbers in the draw on
OL,18,FApril 6 were: 27, 36, 39, 48, 57 and
OL,19,F59.
